page.title: 17Flora of W.C.P.S. Woodland 1
page.content:
{The school woodland}was established 12 years ago .We have identified all the grasses,flowers, plants shrubs and trees that were growing in 1985. It has had trees and shrubs planted in it by children, parents and staff. The other plants have colonised it.
{Grasses Red Fescue, Yorkshire Fog, Perennial Ryegrass, Rough Meadow Grass, Crested Dogstail, Tall Oat Grass, Cocksfoot, Cocksfoot, Creeping Soft Grass, Barred Brome, Meadow Foxtail, Timothy, Common Bent, Couch Grass, Onion Couch.
